author: Russell Brand
description:
Marjorie Taylor Greene lays out her warning to the Republican Party—deliver on promises to hold the powerful accountable or risk losing the trust of their base forever. We discuss the dangers of dangling “deep state” rhetoric without action, the economic struggles crushing younger generations, and how failure could open the door for a new, more extreme form of leadership to take root in America.
